1
00:00:20,090 --> 00:00:20,890
You're awake?

2
00:00:22,510 --> 00:00:24,110
I knew it wasn't like this.

3
00:00:24,850 --> 00:00:26,090
You wouldn't do this.

4
00:00:31,110 --> 00:00:32,409
My guess was right.

5
00:00:33,640 --> 00:00:35,970
Shrimpie has two consciousnesses
in his mind.

6
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:37,760
I don't know why,

7
00:00:38,210 --> 00:00:39,740
but besides his original self,

8
00:00:39,740 --> 00:00:41,520
there's another dark presence inside him—

9
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:42,280
like

10
00:00:43,490 --> 00:00:45,140
two completely separate personalities.

11
00:00:45,140 --> 00:00:46,170
They

12
00:00:46,890 --> 00:00:49,500
share sight, hearing, and touch,

13
00:00:50,700 --> 00:00:53,000
but they don't know each other's
memories or thoughts.

14
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,130
I call that evil side

15
00:00:55,250 --> 00:00:56,680
"Dark Shrimp."

16
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,840
He's been watching

17
00:00:59,380 --> 00:01:02,040
and controlling
Shrimpie's body all this time.

18
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:04,310
Most of the time,

19
00:01:05,349 --> 00:01:07,480
Shrimpie is like a prisoner
trapped inside his own mind,

20
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,680
He can't do anything.

21
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:14,640
Did he go crazy

22
00:01:15,070 --> 00:01:16,280
from snake venom?

23
00:01:18,430 --> 00:01:20,250
It sounds crazy, right?

24
00:01:21,570 --> 00:01:22,940
I would go crazy too.

25
00:01:23,370 --> 00:01:25,200
But he never gave up—

26
00:01:25,930 --> 00:01:27,480
he's been fighting back this whole time.

27
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:30,200
And this Dark Shrimp seems to be plotting
something huge.

28
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,640
Shrimpie wants to stop him

29
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,590
from killing him.

30
00:01:32,590 --> 00:01:34,830
But if that other consciousness
takes control of his body—

31
00:01:34,830 --> 00:01:37,430
then wouldn't he be unable even
to kill himself?

32
00:01:37,430 --> 00:01:40,690
So how is he supposed to destroy
that other consciousness?

33
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:42,160
You're Mo Yungao, right?

34
00:01:42,430 --> 00:01:43,680
Your men are all dead.

35
00:01:44,729 --> 00:01:46,330
The Hidden Thread strategy.

36
00:01:47,259 --> 00:01:48,750
I set up a clue,

37
00:01:49,070 --> 00:01:49,729
and

38
00:01:50,570 --> 00:01:53,370
you'll follow this clue
to think and investigate,

39
00:01:53,450 --> 00:01:54,780
and reach a conclusion.

40
00:01:55,350 --> 00:01:56,370
But in reality, both the conclusion

41
00:01:56,370 --> 00:01:58,229
and the entire chain of reasoning

42
00:01:58,370 --> 00:01:59,340
were traps

43
00:02:00,290 --> 00:02:02,090
I laid out for you from the start.

44
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:04,890
Shrimpie wants to set up a trap

45
00:02:05,220 --> 00:02:06,700
convincing enough that Dark Shrimp
will believe it completely

46
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:08,229
and end up killing himself.

47
00:02:09,130 --> 00:02:10,930
And when that happens, Shrimpie

48
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:12,870
will die with him.

49
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:19,310
But wouldn't Dark Shrimp know everything

50
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:20,600
Zhang Haixia does?

51
00:02:21,410 --> 00:02:23,270
He can't let him notice anything.

52
00:02:24,130 --> 00:02:25,400
How is that possible?

53
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,530
Now two consciousnesses

54
00:02:27,530 --> 00:02:29,260
are fighting for the same body.

55
00:02:29,620 --> 00:02:32,020
Dark Shrimp wants to wipe out
Shrimpie's consciousness.

56
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:33,530
Shrimpie needs to let Dark Shrimp

57
00:02:33,530 --> 00:02:35,190
know where his weakness is,

58
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,010
which is the way to wipe him out.

59
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,360
Step two,

60
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,340
Shrimpie pretends not to know

61
00:02:41,690 --> 00:02:42,579
and reacts as usual.

62
00:02:42,579 --> 00:02:45,110
This way, Dark Shrimp
will fall into the trap.

63
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:47,600
Shrimpie's weakness is me and Mentor.

64
00:02:49,530 --> 00:02:51,140
If his closest ones

65
00:02:52,530 --> 00:02:53,430
betray him

66
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:55,280
and abandon him,

67
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:58,270
it's fatal to him.

68
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:08,740
So this Dark Shrimp
goes around killing people

69
00:03:08,740 --> 00:03:10,600
and intentionally shows it to me.

70
00:03:11,620 --> 00:03:13,630
Sometimes it even pretends those killings
are for my sake.

71
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:14,910
It's trying to provoke me,

72
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:16,090
to push me away from him,

73
00:03:16,090 --> 00:03:17,150
to make me hate him—

74
00:03:18,370 --> 00:03:19,970
so Shrimpie will break down.

75
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:25,720
The cruelest part

76
00:03:26,579 --> 00:03:28,050
of this trap is here.

77
00:03:28,870 --> 00:03:30,740
Obviously it's a trap he set himself,

78
00:03:30,740 --> 00:03:32,400
but he has to be in it too,

79
00:03:32,740 --> 00:03:34,710
and helplessly watch himself

80
00:03:36,470 --> 00:03:37,329
being tortured

81
00:03:38,410 --> 00:03:39,210
until he dies.

82
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:41,950
He can't do anything.

83
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:44,420
Then doing this

84
00:03:44,740 --> 00:03:47,090
can only kill Zhang Haixia's
consciousness.

85
00:03:47,090 --> 00:03:49,250
How do we kill Dark Shrimp's
consciousness?

86
00:03:49,250 --> 00:03:51,470
I guess he needs me to cooperate with him.

87
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:52,300
Then how

88
00:03:53,060 --> 00:03:54,090
do you cooperate?

89
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:06,440
Now I need to know what Dark Shrimp is,

90
00:04:07,930 --> 00:04:09,220
what his weakness is,

91
00:04:09,250 --> 00:04:10,650
and more of his memories.

92
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,220
Was he crazy just now,

93
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:30,180
talking nonsense all the time?

94
00:04:30,180 --> 00:04:31,750
But if what he said is true,

95
00:04:33,620 --> 00:04:34,740
then Zhang Haixia

96
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:38,820
is too pitiful.

97
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:53,440
Shrimpie!

98
00:06:19,010 --> 00:06:25,620
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

99
00:06:25,890 --> 00:06:28,570
[Episode 33]

100
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:49,159
These murals

101
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:53,280
record the history
of the ancient Wupi people.

102
00:07:54,130 --> 00:07:57,060
I should be able to
find the origin of the Dark Shrimp.

103
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,010
These tribes

104
00:07:59,030 --> 00:08:01,960
lived in the southwestern rainforests
year-round,

105
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,480
isolated from the world,

106
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,130
and lived inside the mountains.

107
00:08:05,130 --> 00:08:06,310
Until one day,

108
00:08:06,650 --> 00:08:08,560
their ancestors dug out a huge black stone

109
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,480
from the mountain,

110
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,920
which completely changed the life

111
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,430
of the whole tribe.

112
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,950
To be exact,

113
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:17,690
this stone somehow affected them,

114
00:08:18,250 --> 00:08:20,210
making them bloody and brutal.

115
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:22,810
Their physical functions
also became exceptionally strong,

116
00:08:22,810 --> 00:08:25,270
able to heal themselves without treatment,

117
00:08:25,300 --> 00:08:26,700
and even come back to life

118
00:08:26,770 --> 00:08:27,720
after death.

119
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,720
The medicine that made Shrimpie

120
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,410
recover and go crazy

121
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,789
came from this black stone.

122
00:08:36,580 --> 00:08:37,370
No, wait.

123
00:08:37,530 --> 00:08:38,929
Didn't you tell me before

124
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:41,970
that it was some kind of
worm from jellyfish?

125
00:08:42,890 --> 00:08:44,140
Maybe this thing

126
00:08:46,010 --> 00:08:47,830
originated from here.

127
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:56,400
The black stones are irradiating the soil,

128
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,590
causing a parasite to mutate.

129
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,050
It's the worm Mentor mentioned,

130
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:05,170
called Caiyou worms.

131
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:08,570
All parasitized creatures

132
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:11,780
will also undergo
varying degrees of mutation.

133
00:09:12,100 --> 00:09:13,700
Among them, infected people

134
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,130
become physically strong

135
00:09:15,130 --> 00:09:16,640
and are called Atianre,

136
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:19,900
meaning

137
00:09:21,770 --> 00:09:22,960
"the Chosen One".

138
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,680
After the tribe dug out the black stone,

139
00:09:27,230 --> 00:09:29,090
the Caiyou worms began to spread.

140
00:09:32,390 --> 00:09:34,050
It made snakes grow black hair

141
00:09:34,940 --> 00:09:36,470
and speak human language.

142
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:41,340
It also turned grass into toxic weed.

143
00:09:42,950 --> 00:09:45,950
All parasitized creatures
have one characteristic,

144
00:09:48,650 --> 00:09:51,310
which is that they can hibernate
for a long time.

145
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:54,580
This is the so-called suspended animation.

146
00:09:54,630 --> 00:09:56,160
So the black-haired snakes

147
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,400
and Twilight Grass all come from Nanqiang.

148
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:02,940
They mutated
after being infected with worms.

149
00:10:02,940 --> 00:10:04,320
No wonder the Twilight Grass

150
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,600
grows so luxuriantly here.

151
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,890
It seems these ancient Wupi people

152
00:10:06,890 --> 00:10:08,990
discovered these natural phenomena

153
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,210
and made use of them,

154
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:12,150
using them as weapons

155
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,860
to wipe out other tribes

156
00:10:14,100 --> 00:10:16,500
and continuously expand their territory.

157
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:17,770
But this tribe

158
00:10:17,770 --> 00:10:19,380
has no records or legends.

159
00:10:20,530 --> 00:10:22,860
It must have disappeared for some reason.

160
00:10:28,530 --> 00:10:29,990
The reason should be here.

161
00:10:31,410 --> 00:10:33,390
In fact, the behavior of these Atianre

162
00:10:33,390 --> 00:10:34,990
was controlled by the worms.

163
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:41,120
These Atianre seemed to
have two consciousnesses

164
00:10:43,940 --> 00:10:46,620
fighting each other in the same body.

165
00:10:50,500 --> 00:10:51,100
In the end,

166
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:54,120
they became completely brutal and bloody,

167
00:10:54,860 --> 00:10:57,320
turning into completely different people.

168
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:06,110
So what you did

169
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,530
was not your intention.

170
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:21,650
What's more terrifying is that

171
00:11:21,870 --> 00:11:23,400
over time,

172
00:11:23,650 --> 00:11:24,780
these Atianre

173
00:11:25,030 --> 00:11:27,150
would eventually turn into monsters

174
00:11:27,700 --> 00:11:29,500
because of the worm's power.

175
00:11:30,010 --> 00:11:32,610
And all creatures infected
with Caiyou worms,

176
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,650
like mantises infected with
horsehair worms

177
00:11:35,650 --> 00:11:37,390
that must enter the water,

178
00:11:37,940 --> 00:11:39,280
will desperately

179
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:41,630
want to return to the meteorite.

180
00:11:41,950 --> 00:11:43,880
The occurrence of this phenomenon

181
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:46,250
made the people in the tribe realize

182
00:11:46,530 --> 00:11:47,270
that Atianre

183
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:49,520
did not gain any good power.

184
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:50,790
Its essence

185
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,520
was actually a devil.

186
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:54,460
So the ancient people

187
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:55,300
and Atianre

188
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,130
went to war.

189
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:05,090
The kind ancient Wupi people

190
00:12:05,290 --> 00:12:07,410
were almost all killed
by the cruel Atianre,

191
00:12:07,410 --> 00:12:09,670
the ones who worshipped the black stone.

192
00:12:13,070 --> 00:12:14,730
However, it didn't end there.

193
00:12:19,700 --> 00:12:20,830
The Zhang family...

194
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,710
Our ancestors

195
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,290
noticed something strange in Nanqiang,

196
00:12:25,290 --> 00:12:27,220
and helped the ancient Wupi people

197
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:29,050
fight against the evil Atianre.

198
00:12:29,580 --> 00:12:31,270
These ghost-like creatures

199
00:12:31,910 --> 00:12:33,840
fled all the way to the black stone.

200
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:36,860
They, along with the black stone,

201
00:12:36,890 --> 00:12:40,150
were sealed in a Bronze Ball Mechanism
by the Zhang family.

202
00:12:42,250 --> 00:12:43,870
They never appeared again.

203
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:47,930
An earthquake in Nanqiang 20 years ago

204
00:12:48,580 --> 00:12:50,700
loosened the seal
of the Bronze Ball Mechanism,

205
00:12:50,700 --> 00:12:52,230
and many monsters escaped.

206
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:55,840
The current chief came to handle it

207
00:12:55,860 --> 00:12:57,370
and sealed it again.

208
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,200
I see.

209
00:13:02,990 --> 00:13:03,940
So Dark Shrimp's goal

210
00:13:03,940 --> 00:13:06,270
is to open the Bronze Ball Mechanism again

211
00:13:06,390 --> 00:13:07,990
and return to the meteorite.

212
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,080
Yes.

213
00:13:10,290 --> 00:13:13,050
Behind Dark Shrimp
is the consciousness of the Caiyou worms.

214
00:13:13,050 --> 00:13:15,390
Opening the Bronze Ball Mechanism
is its instinct.

215
00:13:15,390 --> 00:13:17,920
But once the Bronze Ball Mechanism
is opened,

216
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:20,790
all the creatures sealed
inside will come out.

217
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,390
If so,

218
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,170
not only Nanqiang,

219
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:27,360
but everyone will be threatened.

220
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,240
If people are parasitized

221
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:30,790
by the things on this stone,

222
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:33,720
they will become bloodthirsty and brutal.

223
00:13:42,150 --> 00:13:44,280
First, it's consciousness invasion.

224
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,420
Eventually, they undergo

225
00:13:47,050 --> 00:13:51,180
a complete mutation into monsters
resembling human-headed centipedes.

226
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:03,640
Twilight Grass and the Evil God

227
00:14:04,940 --> 00:14:07,670
are enough to turn the outside world
upside down.

228
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:08,980
Such monsters

229
00:14:10,510 --> 00:14:12,460
had better die underground.

230
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,320
Mentor.

231
00:14:38,370 --> 00:14:39,360
Traitor.

232
00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:46,340
Do you think what you burned
was the real medicine?

233
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,270
Zhang Haixia,

234
00:15:11,170 --> 00:15:12,620
I want to rest.

235
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:18,480
Help me end this.

236
00:15:20,530 --> 00:15:22,460
I'll wait for you on the other side.

237
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:51,360
You never give me peace.

238
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:58,690
Do you think
what you burned was the real medicine?

239
00:18:12,660 --> 00:18:13,290
Shrimpie.

240
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:19,870
Zhang Hailou,

241
00:18:20,940 --> 00:18:21,880
can you hold on?

242
00:18:41,320 --> 00:18:43,650
Someone is detonating explosives below.

243
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,380
It's Zhang Haixia.

244
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,370
He needs to go deep underground

245
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:48,940
to find something sealed by

246
00:18:48,940 --> 00:18:50,040
the Zhang ancestors

247
00:18:50,040 --> 00:18:51,840
and release the monster inside.

248
00:19:04,820 --> 00:19:06,160
Where are you going?

249
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:07,660
I have to stop him.

250
00:19:07,980 --> 00:19:09,110
How will you do that?

251
00:19:09,110 --> 00:19:10,320
I don't know yet.

252
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,160
You go first.

253
00:19:34,190 --> 00:19:35,470
We'll catch up later.

254
00:20:01,830 --> 00:20:03,510
It's dangerous, go!

255
00:20:04,900 --> 00:20:05,970
Hold on to me.

256
00:20:07,570 --> 00:20:09,960
Let go, or you'll die!

257
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:10,780
Hold on tight.

258
00:20:11,250 --> 00:20:12,710
I won't let go even if I die.

259
00:20:15,740 --> 00:20:17,470
Do you really like me that much?

260
00:20:19,510 --> 00:20:20,460
I do.

261
00:20:23,240 --> 00:20:24,510
Then if we make it out,

262
00:20:25,590 --> 00:20:26,740
will you marry me?

263
00:21:18,590 --> 00:21:19,520
Adjutant Zhang,

264
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:22,500
is this the secret deep within Nanqiang?

265
00:21:22,650 --> 00:21:24,050
What exactly is in there?

266
00:21:25,110 --> 00:21:27,040
Your mission is already complete.

267
00:23:56,510 --> 00:23:57,700
You're not dead?

268
00:23:59,130 --> 00:24:01,130
How could I bear to die before you do?

269
00:24:58,530 --> 00:25:00,530
You want to use Zhang Haixia's blood

270
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:03,240
to open the Zhang family's seal.

271
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:06,310
He is special.

272
00:25:09,660 --> 00:25:11,640
But his willpower was so strong,

273
00:25:11,670 --> 00:25:12,840
and he was so clever,

274
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:15,920
I have to erase him.

275
00:25:17,210 --> 00:25:18,270
Zhang Hailou.

276
00:25:18,850 --> 00:25:19,920
If you kill me,

277
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:23,180
he will die too.

278
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:29,340
You are not him.

279
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:32,980
Don't call my name.

280
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:43,130
Do you want to go back to Xiacheng?

281
00:27:48,430 --> 00:27:52,280
♪ The setting sun sinks low into the sea ♪

282
00:27:49,560 --> 00:27:51,220
Do you want to go back to Xiacheng?

283
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:52,620
Nonsense, of course I do.

284
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:55,070
Go back to Xiacheng

285
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:57,200
♪ And the ship goes down into the flames ♪

286
00:27:55,550 --> 00:27:56,680
and find our mentor.

287
00:27:57,900 --> 00:27:58,590
Leave me alone!

288
00:27:58,550 --> 00:28:01,090
♪ You're standing by my side ♪

289
00:27:59,300 --> 00:28:00,390
Follow me.

290
00:28:00,440 --> 00:28:02,760
We'll make a name for ourselves
in Balongzhou.

291
00:28:02,760 --> 00:28:04,270
Then we'll return to Xiacheng in glory

292
00:28:04,270 --> 00:28:05,850
and see Mentor together. Let's go!

293
00:28:04,390 --> 00:28:08,190
♪ Time is like a plague,
devouring yesterday ♪

294
00:28:06,270 --> 00:28:07,700
Zhang Haixia, what are you doing?

295
00:28:07,700 --> 00:28:09,520
I don't want to go back to Xiacheng.

296
00:28:09,520 --> 00:28:11,140
I have nothing left to hold me there.

297
00:28:10,330 --> 00:28:12,840
♪ Yet I've searched through
every archive ♪

298
00:28:11,570 --> 00:28:12,740
Go back in my place.

299
00:28:14,590 --> 00:28:16,290
♪ Filled with endless lies ♪

300
00:28:14,700 --> 00:28:16,300
We still came back together.

301
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,530
You shouldn't have come back to save me.

302
00:28:18,300 --> 00:28:20,240
♪ Even behind a thousand masks ♪

303
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:21,030
Didn't you save me too?

304
00:28:20,650 --> 00:28:24,790
♪ In a fleeting moment,
I fear a familiar face ♪

305
00:28:21,940 --> 00:28:22,940
You are my junior.

306
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:25,680
It's my duty to keep you safe.

307
00:28:26,350 --> 00:28:28,180
♪ Fate got one thing wrong ♪

308
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:32,450
♪ Beneath the setting sun,
our shadows overlap ♪

309
00:28:30,080 --> 00:28:31,530
[Nanyang Maritime Supervisory Office]

310
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,050
Hailou,

311
00:28:32,530 --> 00:28:33,460
one day

312
00:28:34,410 --> 00:28:38,540
♪ The wind carries away the goodbye
we never said ♪

313
00:28:34,790 --> 00:28:36,450
you'll have to act on your own.

314
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:38,840
I won't be by your side.

315
00:28:39,370 --> 00:28:42,160
♪ The butterfly upon your shoulder ♪

316
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:42,240
No one will be watching over you.

317
00:28:42,980 --> 00:28:49,150
♪ Stayed with you to witness
this bustling world ♪

318
00:28:50,490 --> 00:28:54,700
♪ Where ruin and decay begin to turn around ♪

319
00:28:55,380 --> 00:28:58,290
♪ A gut feeling of destiny ♪

320
00:28:57,860 --> 00:29:01,490
[iKiwi Film Company]

321
00:28:58,870 --> 00:29:04,930
♪ Bright sunlight, unseen mountains and seas ♪

322
00:29:06,110 --> 00:29:06,900
Thank you.

323
00:29:22,370 --> 00:29:23,610
I'm a little tired.

324
00:29:24,300 --> 00:29:28,380
♪ A reckless faith, blurred from sight ♪

325
00:29:30,490 --> 00:29:33,400
♪ Just to see you once again ♪

326
00:29:34,340 --> 00:29:37,100
♪ The tragedy repeats ♪

327
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:37,810
My name is Zhang Haixia—

328
00:29:38,410 --> 00:29:40,030
♪ For years, a wanderer of Xianyang ♪

329
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:40,560
the xia from "xia ke" (hero).

330
00:29:40,640 --> 00:29:44,780
♪ Bound to the prophecy of thrush and snake ♪

331
00:29:40,710 --> 00:29:41,990
And he's Zhang Hailou—

332
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:44,000
the lou from "louyu" (building).

333
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:45,860
A tower in spring rain overnight.

334
00:29:46,220 --> 00:29:47,810
Xianyang wanderers, years gone by.

335
00:29:46,330 --> 00:29:48,280
♪ Yet suddenly before my eyes ♪

336
00:29:48,690 --> 00:29:52,430
♪ That hurried goodbye ♪

337
00:29:54,650 --> 00:29:58,800
♪ The opening pages of this story
are woven from deceit ♪

338
00:29:59,320 --> 00:30:02,240
♪ A trial written into fate ♪

339
00:30:02,990 --> 00:30:09,040
♪ Through the mist I search your face—
are you still the same? ♪

340
00:30:10,460 --> 00:30:14,800
♪ The wind carries away the goodbye
we never said ♪

341
00:30:15,320 --> 00:30:18,390
♪ The butterfly upon your shoulder ♪

342
00:30:18,780 --> 00:30:24,700
♪ Stayed with you to witness
this bustling world ♪

343
00:31:04,100 --> 00:31:06,480
[A few days later]

344
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:38,590
[Soul-Cleansing Temple]

345
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:54,940
Why are you here?

346
00:32:04,700 --> 00:32:05,880
I was a bit curious,

347
00:32:06,770 --> 00:32:08,030
so I did some research.

348
00:32:09,180 --> 00:32:11,040
What exactly is that black stone,

349
00:32:11,950 --> 00:32:14,080
and what is controlling Zhang Haixia?

350
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:15,460
Did you find anything?

351
00:32:25,330 --> 00:32:27,440
The strange star is three feet across,

352
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:29,090
shaped like a round jade,

353
00:32:29,110 --> 00:32:30,710
and colored like black jade.

354
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:43,610
What does that mean?

355
00:32:42,950 --> 00:32:43,750
[Three Generations—Star Guide Chronicles,
Vol. 1]

356
00:32:43,900 --> 00:32:45,440
I guess that black stone

357
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:47,010
is very likely a meteorite

358
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:49,460
that fell from the sky a long time ago.

359
00:32:49,810 --> 00:32:50,680
A meteorite?

360
00:32:51,050 --> 00:32:52,590
Three-corpse bugs
reside in the Big Dipper;

361
00:32:52,590 --> 00:32:55,320
when stars fall,
the bugs enter the mortal realm.

362
00:32:58,050 --> 00:32:59,330
Actually, among these books,

363
00:32:59,330 --> 00:33:00,860
many are about meteorites.

364
00:33:03,220 --> 00:33:04,010
I suspect

365
00:33:05,070 --> 00:33:06,730
the Caiyou worms on the murals

366
00:33:07,030 --> 00:33:09,290
are the alien bugs
brought by the meteorite.

367
00:33:09,290 --> 00:33:11,090
They have parasitic abilities.

368
00:33:11,420 --> 00:33:12,420
When they parasitize

369
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:13,440
a living creature,

370
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:15,610
they can also help
repair its damaged body.

371
00:33:15,610 --> 00:33:17,070
But there's a side effect.

372
00:33:17,510 --> 00:33:20,250
That is, they will disrupt
the host's nervous system.

373
00:33:20,250 --> 00:33:21,780
And this new consciousness

374
00:33:22,140 --> 00:33:24,600
gradually erodes the host's original mind,

375
00:33:25,610 --> 00:33:27,270
eventually becoming
the new dominant consciousness.

376
00:33:27,270 --> 00:33:28,290
Like

377
00:33:28,980 --> 00:33:30,110
a cuckoo in the nest?

378
00:33:34,900 --> 00:33:35,530
Then,

379
00:33:36,250 --> 00:33:38,960
Zhang Haixia insisting on
returning to Nanqiang earlier

380
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:40,360
was also because of this?

381
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:42,400
This might have something to do with

382
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:44,940
the homing instinct of these alien bugs.

383
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:46,640
Perhaps these alien bugs have

384
00:33:47,900 --> 00:33:49,900
a survival instinct to return home.

385
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:51,030
That's why

386
00:33:51,030 --> 00:33:53,160
he wanted to come to Nanqiang so badly.

387
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:03,380
Where are you going? I'll go with you.

388
00:34:03,380 --> 00:34:04,180
To the toilet.

389
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:05,680
Do you want to follow?

390
00:34:06,850 --> 00:34:07,450
By the way,

391
00:34:07,510 --> 00:34:09,030
the black-haired snake
you mentioned earlier,

392
00:34:09,030 --> 00:34:10,460
did it get on you by accident,

393
00:34:10,460 --> 00:34:13,190
or was it deliberately arranged
by Zhang Haixia?

394
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:17,000
Who knows.

395
00:34:19,260 --> 00:34:21,320
I'm getting married. Are you coming?

396
00:34:21,380 --> 00:34:22,280
Are you coming?

397
00:34:26,510 --> 00:34:28,969
-A happy marriage and kids soon!
-Kids soon!

398
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:34,150
Wish you happiness!

399
00:34:42,860 --> 00:34:43,590
Happy.

400
00:34:43,590 --> 00:34:45,300
Thank you.

401
00:34:46,480 --> 00:34:47,300
One more round!

402
00:34:47,300 --> 00:34:48,110
One more round!

403
00:34:48,110 --> 00:34:49,010
One more round!

404
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:51,300
One more round!

405
00:34:51,460 --> 00:34:52,370
One more round!

406
00:34:52,670 --> 00:34:53,420
One more round!

407
00:34:53,370 --> 00:34:59,290
♪ The past fades into traces on the page ♪

408
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,440
Kids soon!

409
00:34:57,070 --> 00:34:58,480
Congratulations.

410
00:34:58,940 --> 00:34:59,670
From now on,

411
00:35:00,460 --> 00:35:06,240
♪ A silent breeze
brushes past that lingering warmth ♪

412
00:35:00,570 --> 00:35:03,480
you have to carry me on your back
for the rest of your life.

413
00:35:03,480 --> 00:35:04,210
Definitely.

414
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:07,690
Let the feast begin.

415
00:35:07,560 --> 00:35:13,620
♪ In this fleeting world,
I long for a moment of vivid life ♪

416
00:35:08,210 --> 00:35:08,630
Let the feast begin.

417
00:35:08,630 --> 00:35:09,110
Let the feast begin.

418
00:35:09,110 --> 00:35:10,240
Let the feast begin.

419
00:35:14,580 --> 00:35:19,370
♪ I may have a chance to open a door ♪

420
00:35:19,940 --> 00:35:20,500
Come.

421
00:35:20,500 --> 00:35:20,880
Here.

422
00:35:20,650 --> 00:35:27,350
♪ Where love and wish
meet in a fleeting moment ♪

423
00:35:20,960 --> 00:35:22,030
Happy wedding!

424
00:35:22,030 --> 00:35:22,860
Cheers.

425
00:35:22,860 --> 00:35:23,730
Drink up!

426
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:34,220
♪ There's no need to ask questions
in the maze ♪

427
00:35:34,010 --> 00:35:34,760
Eat, eat

428
00:35:34,820 --> 00:35:37,190
♪ The world's bustle ♪

429
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:36,380
Come, eat up.

430
00:35:36,500 --> 00:35:37,230
Don't be shy.

431
00:35:37,630 --> 00:35:42,630
♪ For now, a few of us under the same roof ♪

432
00:35:38,260 --> 00:35:39,390
Let's go over there.

433
00:35:43,620 --> 00:35:49,310
♪ And the story has come to an end ♪

434
00:35:44,550 --> 00:35:45,300
Snake charmer,

435
00:35:45,300 --> 00:35:46,230
shouldn't we have a drink?

436
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:47,340
Absolutely.

437
00:35:47,370 --> 00:35:47,690
Cheers.

438
00:35:47,690 --> 00:35:48,150
Cheers.

439
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:49,840
One more drink.

440
00:35:51,320 --> 00:35:53,250
Aren't you going to ask him to stay?

441
00:35:59,650 --> 00:36:00,650
I didn't expect

442
00:36:00,830 --> 00:36:02,490
everything he said to be true.

443
00:36:02,780 --> 00:36:04,070
He had a very good,

444
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:05,570
great friend.

445
00:36:04,810 --> 00:36:08,010
♪ Clouds drift and fade just a few years ♪

446
00:36:06,710 --> 00:36:08,280
It's hard to imagine what Zhang Haixia

447
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:09,490
has been through.

448
00:36:10,690 --> 00:36:11,990
It must be painful.

449
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:15,100
♪ Mortal world grass
regrows after parting ♪

450
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:15,400
The one left behind at the end

451
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:18,110
suffers the most.

452
00:36:26,900 --> 00:36:29,830
[Years later]

453
00:36:56,020 --> 00:36:57,680
There's trouble in Nanqiang.

454
00:36:58,000 --> 00:36:59,600
We need to work together.

455
00:37:00,450 --> 00:37:03,450
I'm looking forward to
fighting alongside you again.

456
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:47,980
Mentor, Zhang Haichan
is the one who made the mistake.

457
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:49,080
[Zhang Haichan] [Zhang Haidou]

458
00:37:48,010 --> 00:37:49,420
Why are you punishing me?

459
00:37:49,780 --> 00:37:50,900
You are the senior brother.

460
00:37:50,900 --> 00:37:52,500
Her mistake is your mistake.

461
00:37:52,690 --> 00:37:54,210
You need to protect your junior sister,
got it?

462
00:37:54,210 --> 00:37:55,800
I am younger than her.

463
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:58,730
Who told you to become a disciple earlier?

464
00:37:59,510 --> 00:38:01,230
I must have sinned in my past life

465
00:38:01,230 --> 00:38:02,730
to have a junior sister like you.

466
00:38:02,730 --> 00:38:04,070
In the future when I go on missions,

467
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:05,940
I will definitely stay far away from you.

468
00:38:05,940 --> 00:38:07,870
I want to stay far away from you too.

469
00:38:07,870 --> 00:38:09,610
I want to stay far away from you.

470
00:38:09,630 --> 00:38:10,300
-I want to
-Come on, keep up!

471
00:38:10,300 --> 00:38:12,550
-stay far away from you.
-I want to stay far away from you.

472
00:38:12,550 --> 00:38:14,670
-I want to stay far away from you.
-I want to stay far away from you.

473
00:38:14,670 --> 00:38:15,380
Stay away from me!

474
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:18,980
-I want to stay far away from you.
-I want to stay far away from you.

475
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:26,090
Haichan, Haidou,

476
00:38:27,550 --> 00:38:29,280
don't forget what I taught you.

477
00:38:29,340 --> 00:38:31,290
Greet them properly
when we see them later.

478
00:38:31,290 --> 00:38:31,850
Okay.

479
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:41,090
Greetings, chief!

480
00:38:41,190 --> 00:38:41,840
Chief.

481
00:38:53,710 --> 00:38:55,550
Something's happened deep in Nanqiang.

482
00:38:55,550 --> 00:38:56,680
It's time to set off.

483
00:38:56,760 --> 00:38:57,820
Let's set off.

484
00:39:55,670 --> 00:39:59,850
[Wushan Residence]

485
00:40:04,160 --> 00:40:08,140
[Wu Xie]

486
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:07,490
The story of the Southern Archives

487
00:40:07,490 --> 00:40:09,220
has temporarily come to an end.

488
00:40:09,860 --> 00:40:10,920
After watching it,

489
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:11,960
I am just like you,

490
00:40:12,130 --> 00:40:14,060
unable to calm down for a long time.

491
00:40:16,170 --> 00:40:20,790
[Closing Report: Nanyang
Balai Yazhou Salt-Alkali Lake]

492
00:40:16,210 --> 00:40:17,260
My soul

493
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:18,400
seems to have stayed in

494
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:19,880
that sunny Nanyang,

495
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:22,170
that magnificent Bailejing,

496
00:40:20,940 --> 00:40:26,350
[Closing Report: Nanqiang Bailejing]

497
00:40:22,420 --> 00:40:23,620
unwilling to return.

498
00:40:26,350 --> 00:40:33,190
[Closing Report: Panhua Reef]

499
00:40:40,460 --> 00:40:41,340
Has their story

500
00:40:41,610 --> 00:40:42,730
ended here?

501
00:40:46,970 --> 00:40:47,910
Or,

502
00:40:49,030 --> 00:40:50,770
will we be able to meet again?

503
00:41:00,900 --> 00:41:01,530
I think,

504
00:41:02,050 --> 00:41:04,010
in the process of digging into the past,

505
00:41:04,010 --> 00:41:05,740
we will definitely meet again.

506
00:41:05,940 --> 00:41:08,340
I will definitely see their legends again.

507
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:10,090
However,

508
00:41:10,550 --> 00:41:12,880
do you still want to keep
watching with me?

509
00:41:17,150 --> 00:41:27,190
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]
